information: The company F.W. HEMPEL & CO. ERZE UND METALLE (GMBH & CO.), is a Wholesaler, founded in 1941, which operates in the Iron, special grade and pig iron industry. It also operates in the Metals, precious and special, and Iron, pig industries. It is based in Düsseldorf, Germany.
